listings.comment: I was not at all hesitant to use Fiverr, even though this was my first time, because of its stellar reputation. I was a bit wary of who to choose; how ever. I looked around the site and happened upon Noor Ahmed- he offered three price ranges and his star rating was solid- so I picked him and went mid range on the pricing/ man did he deliver. I gave him almost nothing from the start and he, somehow, picked enough information from me to create an extremely professional looking website. He designed my logo, helped me name my company, he basically went above and beyond. I will continue to go back to him throughout this process as I will continue to return to Fiverr. Thank you.

I hired Noor Ahmed for a project, and he delivered the work quickly and followed the instructions as requested. While he met the brief, I found the results to lack creativity and initiative. The work was very standard, not quite polished, and therefore didn’t quite meet my expectations. However, if you're looking for someone to execute exactly what you ask for without deviation, Noor is reliable and efficient.

I could not recommended Noor and his team anymore!! He went above and beyond to cater for my website design needs and my expectations were blown out the window. If you're thinking about doing it, then Noor is your guy. Response time, receptiveness and attention to detail. Cant wait to launch!!

Noor did a phenomenal job, returned a beautiful website very quickly, and was able to adjust and add anything I wanted afterwards. I would recommend him to anyone that is looking to have their website redesigned very well at an affordable price.

Working with seller was easy, simple, everything i needed for my website he gave me in a super timely manner. If i ever need anything again website design related i will come to him. He made my website immensely better.
